同得samsung 合作就緊係用samsung 晶片代工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T11:35:34.000Z","msg":"呢粒C7唔係同SAMSUNG合作個粒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"我錯，我下意識以為amd 手機市場同samsung 合作 ，搵番samsung 代工<br />\n<br />\n而家咁三叔真係食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a0c87407d01efd46095d7bc8527ef1bc6dcdaa9","tid":2050860,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6ef2a0ecfc67f0f6237a14b2f33ed525d617cf","tid":2050860,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T19:09:45.000Z","msg":"AMD供應家用機都夠飽啦"},{"pid":"e3a567374b4d2a59ee117dc1a913fe0626f0ad37","tid":2050860,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"搶埋高通飯碗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dda41df39b86e49cf2fdc5791eafb5c2b11295","tid":2050860,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T01:36:23.000Z","msg":"Fake news嚟"},{"pid":"67b040f0947cdf0fb9b2f1432922d18be08d6f64","tid":2050860,"uid":192940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"篇新聞寫到1999 同埋未fact check<br />\n<br />\n另外個版本係<br />\nAMD 研發顯示核心結合Samsung CPU 兩者合體，用samsung 5nm 工藝，變相Samsung 可以擺脫Mali（最廢）顯示核心，屌打高通、蘋果。所有野仍在吹水階段"}]}